The '''red-fronted coua''' ('''''Coua reynaudii''''') is a species of [[cuckoo]] in the family [[Cuculidae]].
It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[Madagascar]].

Its natural [[habitat]] is subtropical or tropical moist lowland [[forest]]s.

